abstract: MARLBOROUGH, N.Y., Sept. 29.--Jonas Whispell, of Saugerties, Ulster County, recently celebrated his one hundred and second birthday. Considering his years, he is bright mentally and enjoys good health. He is happy in having 52 grandchildren and 34 great-grandchildren living to comfort him in his vigorous old age. Seven of the 15 children which his wife bore him are now living. Mr. Whispell bids fair to live many years yet.

abstract: The Hon. John H.
